<div class="card mt-4">
  <h2>
    Recent updates
  </h2>
  <p class="c-grey-dark">
    Last updated on Friday 02-Apr-2021. If you have Dashboard feedback contact the Simple tech team at help@simple.org.
  </p>
  <% if CountryConfig.current[:name] == "India" %>
    <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
      Week of 03-May-2021
    </h5>
    <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
      <li>
        <p>
          A new download option, "Monthly district data", is available in district reports. It includes end-of-month performance data for all facilities in the district.
        </p>
      </li>
      <li>
        <p>
          We're running a pilot in 3 districts (Punjab, Maharashtra, and Kerala) to capture drug stock data and view drug consumption data in the Dashboard.
        </p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  <% end %>
  <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
    Week of 29-Mar-2021
  </h5>
  <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
    <li>
      <p>
        "BP not controlled" and "Missed visits" cards in "Reports, Overview" now have a "with LTFU" toggle that allows you to see the rates and trends with and without lost to follow-up patients.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
    Week of 15-Mar-2021
  </h5>
  <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
    <li>
      <p>
        "BP controlled", "BP not controlled", and "Missed visits" cards in "Reports, Overview" now exclude lost to follow-up patients by default.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        "BP controlled" card in "Reports, Overview" now has a "with LTFU" toggle that allows you to see BP controlled with and without lost to follow-up patients.
      </p>
    </li>
    <li>
      <p>
        The "Reports, Details" page displays two new cards: "Lost to follow-up" and "Assigned patients breakdown"
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
    Week of 15-Feb-2021
  </h5>
  <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
    <li>
      <p>
        "BP controlled", "BP not controlled", and "Missed visits" sections in "Home" now display subtotal data by facility size.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
    Week of 01-Feb-2021
  </h5>
  <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
    <% if CountryConfig.current[:name] == "India" %>
      <li>
        <p>
          State and block-level reports are now available
        </p>
      </li>
    <% end %>
    <li>
      <p>
        Quickly navigate between reports by using a search bar and search by region or facility name
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <h5 class="font-weight-bold mt-2">
    Week of 25-Jan-2021
  </h5>
  <ul class="mt-3 mb-0">
    <li>
      <p>
        The "BP controlled", "BP not controlled", and "Missed visits" tabs of the "Home" page display overall monthly trends for the last 6 months.
      </p>
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>